---
layout: custom
date: 2025-10-18
ogImage: /assets/img/og/Book_OG.jpg
permalink: /the-nogood-book/
title: The NoGood Book
product_kind: "book"

description: >
  A monograph bringing together five years worth of NoGood illustration projects,
  outlining the backdrop for and context within which my work was created.

# Used in product page marquee
short_title: The NoGood Book
subtitle: false
subtitle_content:

snipcart:
  id: "book-regular-edition"
  price: "70"
  short_description: "The NoGood Book — first edition"
  snipcartimage: "/assets/img/shop/snipcart/Snipcart_NoGoodBook_Regular.png"
  weight: "500"
  # Enable size variants
  size_variant: false
  size_variant_name:
  size_variant_options:

snipcart_print:
  id: "book-regular-edition-print"
  price: "90"
  short_description: "The NoGood Book + print — first edition"
  snipcartimage: "/assets/img/shop/snipcart/Snipcart_NoGoodBook_Regular.png"
  weight: "500"

gallery: # on Single Product page
  - url: "source/assets/img/shop/NoGoodBook_Main.jpg"
    alt: "Illustration of the NoGood Book"
    background_color: "highlight"
    override_blend_mode: true
    padding: false

site:
  # Featured image
  featured_image_url: "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Book_Cover_Featured.jpg"
  featured_image_alt: "The NoGood Book"
  background_color: ""
  override_blend_mode: true
  override_padding: true
  # Include on homepage grid
  featured_product: false
  # Enable tag overlay on featured image
  tag: false
  tag_content: "in production - shipping Q2 2026"
  # Pre-order
  pre_order: false
  # Sold-out
  sold_out: false
  # External link
  external_product: false
  external_product_link: "https://geyser.fund/project/nogoodartbook"
  external_product_title: "Geyser"

# SPECS
specs_intro:
specs:

# SIZE GUIDE
shirt_model:
---

{# TITLE MARQUEE #}
<div class="section">
  <div class="marquee pixel-font header-large uppercase">
    {% if subtitle === true %}
      <ul class="marquee-content">
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ subtitle_content }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ subtitle_content }}</li>
      </ul>
      <ul aria-hidden="true" class="marquee-content">
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ subtitle_content }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ subtitle_content }}</li>
      </ul>
    {% else %}
      <ul class="marquee-content">
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
      </ul>
      <ul aria-hidden="true" class="marquee-content">
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
        <li>{{ short_title }}</li>
      </ul>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>
{# PRODUCT SECTION #}
<div
  id="product" class="section large-grid">
  {# GALLERY #}
  <div class="section-column product-gallery">
    <div class="">
      {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Book_Cover.jpg", "The NoGood Book cover" %}
    </div>
    <div class="">
      {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Close_002.jpg", "Detail shot of the NoGood Book" %}
    </div>
    <div class="video fade-in">
      <video autoplay loop muted playsinline>
        <source src="/assets/img/book/book-shoot.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video>
      </div>
      <div class="slideshow slideshow-8 fade-in">
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_001.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_002.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_003.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_004.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_005.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_006.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_007.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_008.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in">
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Spread_009.jpg", "Spread from the NoGood Book" %}
      </div>
      <div class="fade-in">
        {% image "source/assets/img/book/NG_Shoot_Close_001.jpg", "Detail shot of the NoGood Book" %}
      </div>
      {# BACKGROUND #}
      <div class="posts padding-large bg-muted">
        <div class="padding-right-small">
          <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">
            Background
          </h4>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <p>
            I started working on The NoGood Book in 2024 and decided early to self-publish it, giving me total control over the end
            product—I came up with the book’s concept, designed each and every page, selected the work, hired
            <a href="https://daniel.pizza" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Daniël</a>
            to be my editor and visited various printers to discuss options and budgets. When your order comes in, I’ll ship it with
            care from my studio in Amsterdam.
          </p>
          <p>
            NoGood’s origins lie in the bitcoin space, but this is not a book about bitcoin. It does dedicate ample space to provide
            more background and context about the environment in which my work exists. To achieve this, it’s divided into four
            distinct sections, adding up to 272 pages in total.
          </p>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          {# SECTION LIST #}
          <div class="list three-col-list">
            <div>
              01. Background
            </div>
            <div class="hide-small">
              NoGood’s origins
            </div>
            <div class="align-right text-tabular">
              32 pages
            </div>
            <div class="row-border"></div>
            <div>
              02. Work
            </div>
            <div class="hide-small">
              Showcasing 5 years of illustration projects
            </div>
            <div class="align-right text-tabular">
              128 pages
            </div>
            <div class="row-border"></div>
            <div>
              03. Process
            </div>
            <div class="hide-small">
              Shots from every stage of my process
            </div>
            <div class="align-right text-tabular">
              64 pages
            </div>
            <div class="row-border"></div>
            <div>
              01. Context
            </div>
            <div class="hide-small">
              Articles by people whose work I admire
            </div>
            <div class="align-right text-tabular">
              48 pages
            </div>
            <div class="row-border"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="spacer-extralarge"></div>
        {# VIDEO #}
        <div class="video fade-in">
          <video
            autoplay="autoplay"
            muted="muted"
            loop="loop"
            width="100%"
            height="auto"
            poster="/assets/img/book/Book_Promo_Poster.jpg">
            <source src="/assets/img/book-promo.mp4"></video>
          </div>
          <div class="spacer-large"></div>
          <div class="padding-right-small">
          <p>
            A large chunk of the funds needed to produce the book came from a bitcoin-only crowdfund campaign. I wrote irregular
            updates during the production process, providing a peek behind the scenes while the book’s design kept shapeshifting
            along the way.
          </p>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <h4 class="pixel-font uppercase">Production Updates</h4>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="list tag-list">
            {% for post in collections.post | reverse %}
              {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                {% if tag === "book" %}
                  {% include "source/snippets/list-tag.njk" %}
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          <div class="spacer-extralarge"></div>
          {# MEDIA #}
          {% set mediaItems = collections.clippingsAll | selectattr("book_media", "equalto", true) | list %}
          <h4 class="uppercase pixel-font">Interviews &amp; Coverage ({{ mediaItems | length }})</h4>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <div class="media-list">
            {% set hideCover = true %}
            {% set hideIntro = true %}
            {% for item in mediaItems %}
              {% include "source/snippets/list-clippings.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        {# SPECS #}
        <div class="bg-dark padding-large fade-in">
          <div class="">
            <h4 class="uppercase pixel-font">Specs</h4>
            <div class="spacer"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="list two-col-list specs-list">
            {% for item in bookspecs.specs %}
              <div class="">
                <p>{{ item.title }}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="align-right">
                <p>{{ item.description | safe }}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="row-border"></div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {# PRODUCT INFO #}
      <div class="section-column product-info sticky-two-rows">
        <div class="sticky-wrapper">
          <div
            class="sticky">
            {# BREADCRUMBS #}
            {% include "source/snippets/breadcrumbs.njk" %}
            {# PRICE #}
            <h3 class="pixel-font uppercase">
              {% if site.pre_order === true %}pre-order - shipping Q2 2026{% endif %}
            </h3>
            <div class="spacer"></div>
            {# DESCRIPTION #}
            <p class="text-extra-large">
              A self-published monograph bringing together five years of illustration projects, outlining the backdrop for and context
              within which my work was created.
            </p>
            <div class="spacer-large"></div>
            {# ORDER VARIATIONS #}
            {# COLLECTORS EDITION #}
            <div class="order-option inner-column padding-small outline bg-offwhite">
              <div class="grid large-grid">
                <h3 class="text-large">
                  <s>Collectors edition</s>
                </h3>
                <h3 class="text-large align-right">Sold out</h3>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
            {# REGULAR EDITION #}
            <div class="order-option inner-column outline padding-small">
              <div class="flex-space-between flex-align-start">
                <div class="flex-align-center gap-small">
                  <div class="circle-thumb-group">
                    <div class="circle-thumb">
                      {% image "source/assets/img/shop/NoGoodBook_Cover_Square.jpg", "The NoGood Book cover" %}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-large nowrap">The NoGood Book</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="align-right">
                  <h3 class="text-large pixel-font uppercase">€{{ snipcart.price }}</h3>
                  <p class="text-small">+ shipping</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="spacer"></div>
              {# ORDER BUTTON #}
              {% include "source/snippets/order-button.njk" %}
              <div class="item-description text-small">
                <span id="book-sales-total"></span>
                / {{ booksales.book_run }} available
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
            {# REGULAR EDITION + PRINT #}
            <div class="order-option inner-column outline padding-small">
              <div class="flex-space-between flex-align-start">
                <div class="flex-align-center gap-small">
                  <div class="circle-thumb-group">
                    <div class="circle-thumb">
                      {% image "source/assets/img/shop/NoGoodBook_Cover_Square.jpg", "The NoGood Book cover" %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="circle-thumb">
                      {% image "source/assets/img/shop/NoGoodBook_Print_Icon.jpg", "Included print" %}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-large nowrap">The NoGood Book + print</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="align-right">
                  <h3 class="text-large pixel-font uppercase">€{{ snipcart_print.price }}</h3>
                  <p class="text-small">+ shipping</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="spacer"></div>
              <div class="button-wrapper">
                <a class="snipcart-add-item button pixel-font uppercase" data-item-id="{{ snipcart_print.id }}" data-item-price="{{ snipcart_print.price }}" data-item-url="{{ page.url }}" data-item-description="{{ snipcart_print.short_description }}" data-item-image="{{ snipcart_print.snipcartimage }}" data-item-name="{{ title }} + print" data-item-weight="{{ snipcart_print.weight }}" data-umami-event="add-to-cart" data-umami-event-product="{{ title }} + print">
                  Purchase
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="spacer-small"></div>
              <div class="item-description text-small">
                <span id="print-sales-total"></span>
                / {{ booksales.print_run }} available
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
      const bookRun = {{ booksales.book_run }};
      const printRun = {{ booksales.print_run }};
      const presales = {{ booksales.presales }};
      fetch('https://book-stats.hello-5b9.workers.dev/book-sales')
        .then(r => r.json())
        .then(data => {
          document.getElementById('book-sales-total').textContent = bookRun - (data.total ?? 0);
        })
        .catch(() => {
          document.getElementById('book-sales-total').textContent = bookRun;
        });
      fetch('https://book-stats.hello-5b9.workers.dev/print-sales')
        .then(r => r.json())
        .then(data => {
          document.getElementById('print-sales-total').textContent = printRun - ((data.total ?? 0) + presales);
        })
        .catch(() => {
          document.getElementById('print-sales-total').textContent = printRun - presales;
        });
    </script>